      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "The ○佐倉藩 marker begins the NEXT domain, Sakura-han (a Hotta domain in Shimōsa). Everything to its RIGHT (read first) is Saga's; Sakura's own kokudaka (高 110,000 / 新田高 22,941 / 合高 132,941) prints to its LEFT. The ○ marker is the source's domain-boundary signal — the same teaching point as Satsuma's data overflowing onto Tosa's page."
